Value Filldown local_if (\S+)
Value neighbor_name (.+)
Value neighbor_port (\S+)
Value chassis_id (\S+)
Value mgmt_ip (\S+)

Start
  ^\s*\[${local_if}\]\s*$$
  ^\s*${local_if}\s+has\s+0\s+neighbor\(s\)\s*$$
  ^\s*${local_if}\s+has\s+\d+\s+neighbor\(s\):\s*$$
  ^\s*System\s+name\s*:\s*${neighbor_name}\s*$$
  ^\s*Port\s+ID\s*:\s*${neighbor_port}\s*$$
  ^\s*Chassis\s+ID\s*:\s*${chassis_id}\s*$$
  ^\s*Management\s+address\s*:\s*${mgmt_ip}\s*$$ -> Record

